Reasoning: The paper deals with the problem of identifying frequent patterns in RDF graphs and devises a method to generate a compact representation of the graph. This involves techniques from database systems (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG) to identify and represent patterns. The paper also discusses query processing (cs.IR) and graph algorithms (cs.DS) to evaluate the performance of the proposed approach.
